# Strapi Plugin Development

## Smart Component Filter Plugin Patterns
- Plugin version: v2.0.1
- Location: `apps/strapi/src/plugins/smart-component-filter/`
- Database: PostgreSQL với ratebox schema

## Common Issues & Solutions
- **White screen errors**: Check @strapi/design-system imports
- **Hardcoded data**: Replace with dynamic API calls  
- **Custom fields**: Use React hooks for dynamic loading
- **Real-time filtering**: Implement proper API endpoints

## API Endpoints Pattern
- `/api/smart-component-filter/components` - Get all components
- `/api/smart-component-filter/listing-type/{id}/components` - Filtered components

## Plugin Registration
- Server: Tự động register trong bootstrap
- Admin: Import trong admin/src/index.tsx





- Test APIs với proper authentication